snippet.title: Ali Da Deedar | 13 Rajab Manqabat 2026 | Farhan Ali Waris | Mola Ali Qasida | Qawwali
snippet.description:
13 Rajab Qasida | Ali Da Deedar | 13 Rajab Manqabat 2026 | Farhan Ali Waris | Mola Ali

Syed Farhan Ali Waris Presents 13 Rajab New Manqabat On The Ocassion Wiladat E Imam Maula Ali (as) New Qasida.

Kalam Details |
Title | Aj Kaaby Nu Ali Da Deedar Hogaya
Poetry | Zeeshan Abidi
Additional Variations | SYED FARHAN ALI WARIS
Composition | Hassan Ayaz Jafri, Farhan Ali Waris, Zeeshan Abidi
Chorus | Moshin Hashmi, Safdar Kaleem, Meesum Zaidi, Minhal Rizvi
Audio Recording & Mastered | Meesum Zaidi (LAWA Studio Karachi)
Video | The Focus Studio (Safdar Kaleem)
Chorus | Mohsin Hashmi, Minhal Rizvi, Safdar Kaleem, Mesum Zaidi
Special Thanks | Team FAW

#MolaAli #FarhanAliWaris #AliDadeDaar #13rajab #Manqabat #Qasida #Qawwali

On the blessed occasion of 13 Rajab, under the supremacy of Prophet Muhammad & Bibi Fatima Zahra presents congratulations to imam mahdi on the sacred day of wiladat-e-Imam Ali (A.S.), when Maula Ali was born inside the holy Kaaba, this soulful Manqabat manam ghulam hazrat shah najaf and Qaseeda beautifully reflects the eternal glory of Imam Ali (A.S.), the lion of Allah and the symbol of divine justice. This 13 Rajab Manqabat 2025–2026 and new Qasida of 13 Rajab 2026 expresses the deep spiritual message of Ali ka Ishq, echoing powerful Haider Haider and the timeless truth that . Recited with devotion by , this 13 Rajab Maula Ali new Mankabat dil ali dilbar ali sarwar ali captures the love of Maula Ali (A.S.), celebrating bolo saare ali ali his birth, courage, wilayah and unmatched status in Islam. This tera rajab qasida, 13 Rajab Qasida 2026, and new Manqabat 2026 is a heartfelt tribute for all lovers of Haider-e-Karrar, keeping alive the message of faith, bravery and loyalty that continues from Najaf to Karbala.

بہت خوبصورت کلام ہے! شمس رزاق صاحب کی لکھی ہوئی یہ پنجابی شاعری واقعی جذبات سے بھرپور ہے۔ آپ کی فرمائش کے مطابق میں نے اسے خوبصورت ڈیزائن، ایموجیز اور واضح حصوں میں تقسیم کر دیا ہے تاکہ یہ پڑھنے میں بھی دلکش لگے۔

ساڈے پیار پثالی جئے ہن
لوکی ویکھ کے سڑ بھج گئے ہن 🔥
کجھ کئی دا کدنڑ ونجایائے لوکاں رولا چا پایائے 🗣️

رنگ سوہنا اوہدا جیویں پھل نے گلاب دے 🌷
اکھیاں نے اس دیاں مٹکے شراب دے 🍷
اوتھوں میں وی پیک چا لایائے لوکاں رولا چا پایائے 🥂

اوہ میری میں اس دی جان ہاں ❤️
کر بیٹھے اساں عام اعلان ہاں 📣
اساں باہنہ تے ڈھول سوایائے لوکاں رولا چا پایائے ✨

ٹک ٹاک اوتے ساڈے رولے پئے گئے 🎬
ہتھ نپ کے فوٹو بنایائے لوکاں رولا چا پایائے📸

راہندے شمس رزاق نوں ڈر وے 😟
نکھڑ گئے ڈھولا ویسوں مر وے 🥀
اساں پیار دا گیت چا گایائے لوکاں رولا چا پایائے 🎶 ♫

💔 Dil Ohde Naavin Assan Laaye Lokan Rola Cha Payaye 💔

Loki Vekh Ke Sar Bhuj Gaye Hin 🔥
Kujh Kai Da Kadan’r Vanjaye Lokan Rola Cha Payaye 🗣️

Rang Sohna Ohda Jivein Phull Ne Gulab De 🌷
Akhiyan Ne Iss Diyan Matkay Sharab De 🍷
Othon Main Vi Peg Cha Layaye Lokan Rola Cha Payaye 🥂

snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS 5 SEASON FINALE (2025) | The Rightside Up | Netflix
snippet.description:
#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Stranger Things Season 5 finale brings the story to its epic conclusion as Hawkins faces its darkest hour yet, with Vecna returning and the worlds of the Upside Down and the Rightside Up on the brink of collapse. The Stranger Things 5 official trailer and final season teasers highlight intense battles, emotional reunions, and the ultimate stand led by Eleven, Hopper, Mike, Dustin, Lucas, Will, Max, and the rest of the beloved group. Streaming on Netflix, this final chapter promises high stakes, heartbreaking moments, and a powerful ending to one of the most iconic series of all time.
The inspiration behind this video:
The end of the Upside Down is finally here! In this video, we provide a frame-by-frame breakdown of the explosive Stranger Things Season 5 Trailer, analyzing every hidden detail in the Stranger Things 5 Final Season trailer 2. As Netflix prepares to release the conclusion to its biggest show, the stakes have never been higher for Hawkins. We discuss the terrifying reveal of Vecna (Jamie Campbell Bower) in the Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser and what the footage tells us about the ultimate war for reality. Whether you are searching for the Stranger Things Season 5 release date or just reacting to the intense Stranger Things trailer, this video is your ultimate guide to the final chapter.

The entire cast returns for this emotional farewell. We explore the pivotal destiny of Eleven (Millie Bobby Brown) and her connection to Will Byers (Noah Schnapp). We also dive into the fates of the core group: Mike Wheeler (Finn Wolfhard), Dustin (Gaten Matarazzo), and Lucas (Caleb McLaughlin) as they fight to save Max (Sadie Sink). With Chief Hopper (David Harbour) and Joyce Byers (Winona Ryder) reunited, the adults—including Cara Buono—are ready to stand alongside the older teens: Steve Harrington (Joe Keery), Nancy Wheeler (Natalia Dyer), Jonathan Byers (Charlie Heaton), and Robin (Maya Hawke).

Finally, we address the hype surrounding the finale format. We speculate on the Stranger Things Season 5 Volume 2 trailer and whether the show will have a split release like the previous season. We analyze search trends for Stranger Things Season 5 Part 2 trailer and Stranger Things 5 Volume 2, discussing what the st5 trailer leaks reveal about the ending. If you are looking for Stranger Things 5 trailer volume 2 theories or a full breakdown of the Stranger Things final trailer, we have you covered. Don't miss our predictions on who will survive Stranger Things Season 5.

Massive shoutout to Ish who helped co-host this video, he’s an amazing storyteller and I can’t thank him enough for his time and energy, go check him out: https://youtube.com/@ish

We had thousands of players try to join our first large scale, multi day, competition civilization event in a first come first serve basis. We accepted the first 500 boys and 500 girls who joined in chronological order on the Minecraft server when it went live. If a player broke the rules they agreed to in any way or lied on their application about any information to try and sabotage other players, they were banned by the staff who were monitoring 24/7 after an investigation, their actions were reversed and players they killed were revived, and they were replaced with the next boy or girl in line who had tried to join the server earlier in chronological order.
